<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Leia taksa vakna dingin,
 Guohpi nisa nuoia nasep a ngai,
 A lul zaw thagau vakna ding hin chu,
 Lal nasep hi a ngai.

[V2]
 Van Lal na hi hun le hun lo gen lo a,
 Sep ding ahi;
 Van hehpihna Kalvari a hung lang khan,
 Sem di'n ei hilh.

[V3]
 2. Pulpit ah van thu I gena,
 Ho-In sung maiah thu I zawp ua,
 Mundanga zuou thugena I um hin,
 Lal na sem I hi dem?

[V4]
 3. Bible thu haksa haw genin,
 He kisa'n midangte simmawh leuhing,
 Kingainiem a Krista chu sin loin,
 Lal nasem I hi dem?

[V5]
 4. Krista Chanchin pha gen heng la,
 Ho-In leh mundang ale paucham in;
 Thutak kingakna banin um leu hing,
 Lal na semte hii tiu.</lyrics>
<title>FOR YOU AND FOR ME</title>
<hymn_number>165</hymn_number>
<author>Thangngur</author>
</song>